      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey im having some really bad pains in my stomach... it started right by my belly button a few hours ago but now it has moved down to the bottom right side and it's super sharp and hurts when i move. could it just be bad gas or maybe really bad cramps? i really need to sleep so can i just take some strong ibuprofen or maybe some codeine to numb it so i can pass out?",
